name: Organic Cotton & Hemp Tote Bag (cherry)
description:
This is a handmade bag featuring an original design on the front. Made from sturdy 10 oz organic cotton & hemp cloth (45% cotton, 55% hemp) & lined with fantastic bright red cotton/poly fabric.

The organic cotton and hemp fabric has a beautiful textural quality and natural unbleached colour.
It's also very hard wearing and environmentally friendly.

The fruit design has been heat transferred onto one side. The handles are made from 100% cotton webbing and are 2.5 cm wide (1 inch).

Bag size: 30.5 x 36 cm (12 x 14.2 inches)
Total height with straps: 65.5 cm (25.8 inches)

The bag fits easily over the shoulder and is more than large enough to fit a standard size magazine. Perfect as a market bag, library bag, beach bag, baby bag or just an every day eye-catching accessory!


**CARE INSTRUCTIONS** 
Do not soak or tumble dry.
Do not iron where the image is present.

All amounts are in Australian dollars.
